Package: adc
Type: Package
Title: Calculate Antecedant Discharge Conditions
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Michael", 
             family = "Schramm", 
             email = "mpschramm@gmail.com", 
             role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
             comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1876-6592")),
      person(given = "Nick", 
             family = "Bond",  
             role = "cph", 
             comment = "Author of the hydrostats::baseflow function"))
Maintainer: Michael Schramm <mpschramm@gmail.com>
Description: Calculates some antecedant discharge conditions useful in 
    streamflow and water quality rating curve regression methods. This includes 
    estimated flow anomalies, base flow, and smooth discounted flows calculated 
    using mean daily streamflow measurements.
